++ System Configuration Screen

The SCS is SystemManagement that holds the [Configuration] of all of TheSystem to be accessed. This includes:
    * [Hardware]
    * ApplicationManagement
        * ApplicationCategories
    * SystemComponents
    * [Network]
    * [Memory]
    * UserInterfaces
    * UserRule]s
    * [Users] and [Accounts]

SCS is equivalent to the control panel and YAST.